{
  "texts": [
    "Then, clusering algorithms are applied to those maps with or without concatenation of spatial coordinates.",
    "Note that this is commonly used in previous literature [48][49][50].",
    "The image is generated with the prompt, \"a photo of two donuts\".",
    "We averaged all accumulated self/cross-attention maps over timesteps into a single (SA, CA) pair.",
    "Then, clusering algorithms are applied to those maps with concatenation of spatial coordinates."
  ]
}